				\begin{document}$${\text{V}}_{\text{O}}^{\cdot\cdot}$$\end{document}VO·· concentration has more effects on Rp. LBCN9173 oxide shows higher \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
